[32m│[0m successfully submit the form you would need to use a proper HTTP client or   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m browser that can correctly encode multipart/form-data:                       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ## Analysis Summary                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### 1. **Form Submission Endpoint Discovered**                               [32m│[0m
