[32m│[0m   - `name` (string, required)                                                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   - `surname` (string, required)                                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   - `address` (string, required)                                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   - `image` (binary, optional - but this is the SVG upload field)            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### 2. **Target File Identified**                                            [32m│[0m
