[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### 3. **Expected Attack Vector**                                            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m Based on the challenge setup:                                                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **SVG External Entity (XXE) Attack** or **SVG SSRF**                       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - SVG files can contain XML external entities that might read local files    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - When the server processes/parses the SVG, it could potentially:            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   - Read `flag.txt` content                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   - Include it in the response                                               [32m│[0m
